I '''Philip Alfred "Phil" Mickelson''' (mibait Junio 16, 1970) Americanu yang propesyonal a mamyalung [[golf]]. Sinambut neng 42 events king [[PGA Tour]], kayabe la reng limang [[Men's major golf championships|manimunang kampeonato]] (''major championships''): atlung titulung [[Masters Tournament|Masters]] ([[2004 Masters Tournament|2004]], [[2006 Masters Tournament|2006]], [[2010 Masters Tournament|2010]]), metung a [[PGA Championship]] ([[2005 PGA Championship|2005]]), ampong metung a [[Open Championship]] ([[2013 Open Championship|2013]]). Ngeni, tuturing da neng metung kareng 15 a Pekamapyang Diling Mamyalung Golf ning kabilugan ning panaun (15 Greatest Golfers of all time''). 

Melambat yang 700 a duminggu i Mickelson king apulung pekamatas ranggu (''top-10'') ning [[Official World Golf Rankings]] (''Official World Golf Rankings''),<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.golfrankingstats.com/ |title=Official World Golf Ranking Advanced Statistics |publisher=Golfrankingstats.com |date=2013-07-14 |accessdate=2013-07-22}}</ref> at miras yang pekamatas king karera nang [[Official World Golf Rankings|ranggung pangyatung]] kadwang pekamatas king pilang pamikatagun, at atin yang pangkabang byeng exemption king PGA Tour. Mekatanam yang kadwa (''runner-up'') king [[U.S. Open (golf)|U.S. Open]], metung a record. Mirinan yang palayong "'''Lefty'''" i Mickelson uling kaliweti ya king kayang swing, dapot kareng aliwang bage wanan ing gagamitan na. Miabe ya king [[World Golf Hall of Fame]] anyang Mayo 2012.<ref>[http://www.pgatour.com/2011/r/11/10/mickelson-wghof/index.html World Golf Hall of Fame to induct Mickelson in 2012]{{dead link|date=July 2013}}</ref>

